<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Webov&eacute; str&aacute;nky a v&scaron;echny služby &nbsp;jsou majetkem ABCMobile O&Uuml; (registračn&iacute; č&iacute;slo společnosti: 14710834 a registrovan&aacute; adresa: Harju maakond, Tallinn, Peterburi tee 71-318, 11415, Estonia). ABCMobile O&Uuml; je registrov&aacute;na u spr&aacute;vn&iacute;ho org&aacute;nu Phone-paid Services, kter&yacute; ř&iacute;d&iacute; použ&iacute;v&aacute;n&iacute; telefonn&iacute;ch služeb se zv&yacute;&scaron;enou sazbou.</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Tato z&aacute;sady určuj&iacute;, jak použ&iacute;v&aacute;me a chr&aacute;n&iacute;me ve&scaron;ker&eacute; informace, kter&eacute; poskytnete při použ&iacute;v&aacute;n&iacute; tohoto webu. Jsme zav&aacute;z&aacute;ni zajistit, aby va&scaron;e soukrom&iacute; bylo chr&aacute;něno. Ve&scaron;ker&eacute; informace, kter&eacute; jste poskytli a kter&eacute; mohou v&eacute;st k va&scaron;&iacute; identifikaci, budou použity v souladu s t&iacute;mto prohl&aacute;&scaron;en&iacute;m o ochraně osobn&iacute;ch &uacute;dajů.</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Tyto z&aacute;sady určuj&iacute; n&aacute;sleduj&iacute;c&iacute;:</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">1. Jak&eacute; informace shromažďujeme</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">2. Jak jsou informace využ&iacute;v&aacute;ny</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times N